name: Minotaurohgod
description:
We will go back in time and finish this game later.

Controls

Movement: W A S D
Interact: E

Goal of the Game

Get to the yellow portal door in each maze to reach the next level.
To reach it, you need to travel through time and prevent walls from crumbling or doors from breaking. You can also pick up and replant saplings in different locations.
